  <FLAVOURTEXT>
    <LOCALISED_TEXT LanguageCode="en-US"><![CDATA[With the armory of light, even the squire may champion her people.]]></LOCALISED_TEXT>
    <LOCALISED_TEXT LanguageCode="fr-FR"><![CDATA[Avec l’armurerie de la lumière, même une écuyère peut devenir la championne de son peuple.]]></LOCALISED_TEXT>
    <LOCALISED_TEXT LanguageCode="es-ES"><![CDATA[Armada con la luz, hasta la escudera podría defender a su pueblo.]]></LOCALISED_TEXT>
    <LOCALISED_TEXT LanguageCode="de-DE"><![CDATA[Mit einem Arsenal aus Licht kann selbst ein Junker sein Volk anführen.]]></LOCALISED_TEXT>
    <LOCALISED_TEXT LanguageCode="it-IT"><![CDATA[Con l’armeria di luce, perfino la scudiera può difendere il suo popolo.]]></LOCALISED_TEXT>
    <LOCALISED_TEXT LanguageCode="jp-JA"><![CDATA[光の武装をまとい、その従者は人々の勇者となる。]]></LOCALISED_TEXT>
    <LOCALISED_TEXT LanguageCode="ko-KR"><![CDATA[빛으로 만든 갑옷을 입으면 일개 종자도 민중을 위해 싸우는 영웅이 될 수 있다.]]></LOCALISED_TEXT>
    <LOCALISED_TEXT LanguageCode="ru-RU"><![CDATA[Вооруженный светом, даже оруженосец способен защитить свой народ.]]></LOCALISED_TEXT>
    <LOCALISED_TEXT LanguageCode="pt-BR"><![CDATA[Com um arsenal de luz, até mesmo a escudeira pode defender seu povo.]]></LOCALISED_TEXT>
  </FLAVOURTEXT>
  <TYPE metaname="Enchantment" />
  <SUB_TYPE metaname="Aura" order_de-DE="0" order_es-ES="0" order_fr-FR="0" order_it-IT="0" order_jp-JA="0" order_ko-KR="0" order_pt-BR="0" order_ru-RU="0" />
